These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: yellow, grey, lilac
1. the person who likes grey is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
2. the person who likes yellow is on the far right##1
3. the person who likes yellow is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Color   | lilac | grey | yellow |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: reading, writing, chess
1. the person who's hobby is writing is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Hobby   | reading | chess | writing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, western, family
1. the person watching western movies is in an even position##4
2. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person watching family movies##3
3. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Movie-Genre   | action | western | family |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-4::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  police-officer, fisherman, entrepreneur
1. the fisherman is in an odd position##4
2. the entrepreneur is on the left of the fisherman##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |  3   |
| Job   | police-officer | entrepreneur | fisherman |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-5::.
